jokes.text: I went to buy some camo pants but couldn’t find any.
I always find elevator jokes to be uplifting.
Most people are shocked when they find out how bad I am as an electrician.
I’ve had a perfectly wonderful evening, but this wasn’t it.
I failed math so many times at school, I can’t even count
I tried to walk into a Target, but I missed.
My fake plants died because I forgot to fake water them
I'm against picketing, but I don't know how to show it
I haven't slept for ten days, because that would be too long
I was addicted to the Hokey Pokey, but I turned myself around

I used to play piano by ear, but now I use my hands
